reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works with a Doorbell Camera!
reviews.reviewText: My camera system is on a UPS so I can still view it even during a power outage. Yes, the Wi-Fi is on a UPS too, so all the wireless devices work on battery backup. However, my doorbell camera would go offline since it gets power from the doorbell transformer. Running the cabling into my network closet to the UPS and this transformer solved that issue. If the power goes out I can still hear my doorbell AND see who is there. This transformer should work fine if you have a simpler setup too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Works as expected
reviews.reviewText: I got this because I did not have the common "C" wire for my Nest smart thermostat. It provides 24V 0.5A and is a great solution for providing stable constant power to your thermostat. The alternative way was to crawl into the attic and install a new cable myself which is a big hassle or hire someone to do it for a lot of money. So this little transformer provides a cheap solution. My only complaint is that there were no instructions. However, it is very easy to find some guidance online. Overall I recommend this transformer if you want to power your doorbell, camera, or smart thermostat.
